Events that occurred on 26 June.

content.title: On Earth
content.content:
1957 - J.R.R. Tolkien writes a letter to Deirdre Levinson.
1968 - J.R.R. Tolkien writes Letter 305.
2007 - Tree of Tales is published.
2010 - The Tolkien Society's Northern Hemisphere seminar: "Tolkien & Birmingham".
2012 - Tolkien and Welsh by Mark T. Hooker is published.
2016 - Scholar John Ellison dies.
